Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic recorded a triple-double with 23 points, 17 rebounds, and 15 assists
The Nuggets finished a perfect 21 of 21 from the free throw line
They also set a season-high in assists with 44
Young now has five or more assists in 193 straight regular season games. It's the third-longest streak in NBA history, trailing only John Stockton (336) and Isiah Thomas (209).
Post-Match Reflections: It started a busy 17-game month on the right note for Denver
The Nuggets had seven players finish in double figures
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Nuggets broke open the game with a 39-14 run in the third quarter
Young was called for a technical foul during the stretch, and Hunter drew a technical for flopping
